1. *Pričaj* mi o svojim planovima za budućnost. (Tell me about your plans for the future.)

2. Učiteljica je *pričala* o istoriji. (The teacher was talking about history.)

3. Moj otac je *pričao* o svojim putovanjima. (My father was talking about his travels.)

4. *Priča* se da će se ovo desiti. (It is said that this will happen.)

5. Dete je *pričalo* sa svojim prijateljima. (The child was talking to his friends.)

6. Oni su *pričali* dugo. (They were talking for a long time.)